title: Mecklenburg-Schwerin Landtag Elections
new-page: true
tags: event
priority: -2
view-if: (year = mecklenburg_schwerin_election_year and month >= mecklenburg_schwerin_election_month) or (year > mecklenburg_schwerin_election_year)
on-departure: month_actions += 1; mecklenburg_schwerin_election_year = mecklenburg_schwerin_election_year + 4 if mecklenburg_schwerin_snap_election_called == 0; mecklenburg_schwerin_election_year = year + 4 if mecklenburg_schwerin_snap_election_called == 1; mecklenburg_schwerin_election_month = month if mecklenburg_schwerin_snap_election_called == 1; mecklenburg_schwerin_snap_election_called = 0
set-jump: mecklenburg_schwerin_landtag_results

= Mecklenburg-Schwerin Landtag Elections, [+ month : month +] [+ year +]

Mecklenburg-Schwerin holds Landtag elections. This system reuses federal party support, applies Mecklenburg-Schwerin weights, normalizes results, and allocates **51** seats with D'Hondt.

- @calculate_mecklenburg_schwerin_landtag: Count the votes.

@calculate_mecklenburg_schwerin_landtag
on-arrival: mecklenburg_schwerin_government = 1 if mecklenburg_schwerin_government == undefined; mecklenburg_schwerin_leader = "Johannes Stelling" if mecklenburg_schwerin_leader == undefined; mecklenburg_schwerin_majority_cabinet = 0 if mecklenburg_schwerin_majority_cabinet == undefined
go-to: election_algorithm
set-jump: mecklenburg_schwerin_landtag_results

@mecklenburg_schwerin_landtag_results
on-arrival: {! var isMecklenburgSchwerinSnapElection = Number(Q.mecklenburg_schwerin_snap_election_called) === 1; Q.mecklenburg_schwerin_next_election_year_preview = (isMecklenburgSchwerinSnapElection ? (Number(Q.year) || 0) : (Number(Q.mecklenburg_schwerin_election_year) || Number(Q.year) || 0)) + 4; Q.mecklenburg_schwerin_next_election_month_preview = isMecklenburgSchwerinSnapElection ? Q.month : Q.mecklenburg_schwerin_election_month; if (typeof window !== 'undefined' && typeof window.calculateMecklenburgSchwerinLandtagResults === 'function') { window.calculateMecklenburgSchwerinLandtagResults(Q); } !}

= Mecklenburg-Schwerin Landtag election results

Next Mecklenburg-Schwerin election after this Landtag is due in **[+ mecklenburg_schwerin_next_election_month_preview : month +] [+ mecklenburg_schwerin_next_election_year_preview +]**.

Mecklenburg-Schwerin Landtag seats: **[+ mecklenburg_schwerin_landtag_total_seats +] / 51**.

Current Mecklenburg-Schwerin government: **[+ mecklenburg_schwerin_current_government_name +]** ([+ mecklenburg_schwerin_current_government_parties +]) led by **[+ mecklenburg_schwerin_leader +]**.

Current government seats: **[+ mecklenburg_schwerin_current_government_seats +] / 51**. Status: **[+ mecklenburg_schwerin_current_government_status +]**. Majority cabinet: **[+ mecklenburg_schwerin_majority_cabinet +]**.

Current government leverage: **[+ mecklenburg_schwerin_leverage +]**.

{!<table>!}
{!<tr><td>Party</td><td>Mecklenburg-Schwerin vote share</td><td>Seats (out of 51)</td></tr>!}
{!<tr><td><div class="box" style='background-color:#E3000F; outline: 2px; outline-style: solid;'> </div> !} SPD{!</td><td>!} [+ mecklenburg_schwerin_spd_votes_disp +]% {!</td><td>!} [+ mecklenburg_schwerin_spd_r +] {!</td></tr>!}
{!<tr><td><div class="box" style='background-color:#DCCA4A'> </div> !} [+ ddp_name +]{!</td><td>!} [+ mecklenburg_schwerin_ddp_votes_disp +]% {!</td><td>!} [+ mecklenburg_schwerin_ddp_r +] {!</td></tr>!}
{!<tr><td><div class="box" style='background-color:#D5AC27'> </div> !} DVP{!</td><td>!} [+ mecklenburg_schwerin_dvp_votes_disp +]% {!</td><td>!} [+ mecklenburg_schwerin_dvp_r +] {!</td></tr>!}
{!<tr><td><div class="box" style='background-color:#5E8C31'> </div> !} WP{!</td><td>!} [+ mecklenburg_schwerin_wp_votes_disp +]% {!</td><td>!} [+ mecklenburg_schwerin_wp_r +] {!</td></tr>!}
{!<tr><td><div class="box" style='background-color:#3f7bc1'> </div> !} DNVP{!</td><td>!} [+ mecklenburg_schwerin_dnvp_votes_disp +]% {!</td><td>!} [+ mecklenburg_schwerin_dnvp_r +] {!</td></tr>!}
{!<tr><td><div class="box" style='background-color:#8B0000'> </div> !} KPD{!</td><td>!} [+ mecklenburg_schwerin_kpd_votes_disp +]% {!</td><td>!} [+ mecklenburg_schwerin_kpd_r +] {!</td></tr>!}
{!<tr><td><div class="box" style='background-color:#954B00'> </div> !} NSDAP{!</td><td>!} [+ mecklenburg_schwerin_nsdap_votes_disp +]% {!</td><td>!} [+ mecklenburg_schwerin_nsdap_r +] {!</td></tr>!}
{!<tr><td><div class="box" style='background-color:#000'> </div> !} Z{!</td><td>!} [+ mecklenburg_schwerin_z_votes_disp +]% {!</td><td>!} [+ mecklenburg_schwerin_z_r +] {!</td></tr>!}
{!</table>!}

= Choose a Mecklenburg-Schwerin coalition

A coalition is selectable if it controls at least **26** of the **51** Landtag seats. If no listed coalition has a majority, the incumbent Mecklenburg-Schwerin government may continue as a minority cabinet.

- @mecklenburg_schwerin_select_ddp_spd
- @mecklenburg_schwerin_select_spd_ddp_dvp
- @mecklenburg_schwerin_select_dvp_ddp_dnvp_wp
- @mecklenburg_schwerin_select_dvp_dnvp
- @mecklenburg_schwerin_select_dvp_dnvp_wp_nsdap
- @mecklenburg_schwerin_select_dnvp_nsdap
- @mecklenburg_schwerin_select_nsdap_alone
- @new_mecklenburg_schwerin_elections: Call new Mecklenburg-Schwerin Landtag elections.
- @root: Continue without changing the Mecklenburg-Schwerin government.

@mecklenburg_schwerin_select_ddp_spd
title: DDP-SPD
subtitle: DDP + SPD — [+ mecklenburg_schwerin_ddp_spd_coalition_seats +] / 51 — [+ mecklenburg_schwerin_ddp_spd_coalition_status +]
view-if: mecklenburg_schwerin_ddp_spd_coalition_selectable = 1
on-arrival: {! Q.mecklenburg_schwerin_government = 1; if (typeof window !== 'undefined' && typeof window.updateMecklenburgSchwerinCoalitionOptions === 'function') { window.updateMecklenburgSchwerinCoalitionOptions(Q); } !}
go-to: mecklenburg_schwerin_leader_selection

